                  <msItem>
                     <p> Indenture by which <persName>
                           <forename>John</forename> 
                           <surname>Leghes</surname>, the prior of <orgName role="prior" key="org_106005">St. Mary and St. Nicholas of Typtre</orgName>
                        </persName>, 
                  grants, with the assent of the convent, to 
                  <persName>
                           <forename>John</forename> 
                           <surname>Blythe</surname> of <placeName role="person" key="place_106103">Innorde</placeName>
                        </persName>, 
                  one piece of land in <placeName key="place_106080">Great Braxstede</placeName> for 100 years, at an annual rent of 2s.
                  Dated at <placeName role="date" key="place_106178">Toleshunt</placeName> the Thursday before the feast of St. Michael, 
                  <origDate notBefore="1398-06-22" notAfter="1399-06-21">22 Rich. II</origDate>.
                  </p>
